OL,4,Cafter 'dangerous' 45-minute pursuit
OL,6,FA man from Eastleigh who led police
OL,7,Fofficers on a "dangerous" pursuit
OL,8,Facross three counties has been jailed.
OL,10,FSeamus Ford, 22, was reported to
OL,11,Fofficers after he was seen colliding
OL,12,Fwith bins near Wetherspoons near
OL,13,FSalisbury.
OL,15,FHe was then seen by police on Brown
OL,16,FStreet, where he failed to stop.
OL,18,FFord, of the Quadrangle, Eastleigh,
OL,19,Fled police on a 45-minute pursuit
OL,20,Fthrough three counties.
