OL,3,CFootage shows moment police arrest man
OL,4,Cafter 'dangerous' 45-minute pursuit
OL,6,FIn Salisbury Crown Court, Ford pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to dangerous driving, failing
OL,8,Fto provide a specimen for analysis,
OL,9,Fdriving without a licence and
OL,10,Finsurance and possession of heroin and
OL,11,Fcannabis.
OL,13,FHe was jailed for 15 months and
OL,14,Fdisqualified from driving for 19
OL,15,Fmonths.
OL,17,FPC Pedliham, based in Salisbury
OL,18,Fresponse, said: "Ford's driving was
OL,19,Fsome of the worst I've seen and could
OL,20,Fhave resulted in numerous collisions.
